                        <dd><span>第<i>2</i>步</span>通过做空股指期货，对多头组合的β进行对冲。</dd>
                    </dl>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 object-non-visible" data-animation-effect="fadeIn" data-effect-delay="150">
                <img src="/assets/images/img_1.png" alt="" style="margin:20px auto 0" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12 object-non-visible" data-animation-effect="fadeIn" data-effect-delay="200">
                <img src="/assets/images/img_2.png" alt="" style="margin: auto" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
